there’s  a  crisis  in  dealing  with  IUU  vessels—illegal,  unreported, 
unregulated.  They’re  taking  fish  and  taking  literally—and  col-
lecting them when they’re immature, and dumping them in foreign 
markets  that  treat  them  like  sardines  rather  than  salmon.  Now,  I 
can’t add any more money now. Can you do anything? 

Secretary GUTIERREZ. IUU Fishing, associated with stateless ves-
sels  operating  on  the  high  seas  as  well  as  vessels  from  distant- 
