The  CHAIRMAN.  About  6  months  ago,  we  began  seeing,  on  CNN 
and  other  TV  programs,  about  contaminated  pet  food.  Then  it  was 
followed  by  contaminated  toothpaste,  food.  Forty  percent  of  dump-
